1
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,000
You say no more lending,

2
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,520
and it just stops?

3
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,320
How dare you!

4
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,400
How dare you speak to the Magistrate like this!

5
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,720
Lady Ruixi,

6
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,920
Magistrate Shen came here in person today

7
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,760
because of your contributions to Ercheng.

8
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,960
Please watch your tongue.

9
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,960
You people

10
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,000
are full of morality and justice.

11
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:33,960
When you need me, you praise me to the skies.

12
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:38,960
When things go south, you use your authority to suppress me.

13
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,760
Hmph.

14
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:42,200
It's truly disgusting.

15
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,200
Lady Ruixi,

16
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,760
if it has come to this,

17
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,260
I have nothing more to say.

18
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,960
If you refuse to announce the end of lending,

19
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,680
I will do it myself.

20
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,930
What is the meaning of this?

21
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,200
Are you rebelling?

22
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:06,080
Don't be anxious, Magistrate.

23
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:09,760
Let me show you something good.

24
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,720
This is...

25
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:45,200
This flower is named Chilan Bian.

26
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,200
It feeds on human greed.

27
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:48,920
Right now,

28
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:51,440
the greed of the entire city

29
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,360
is nourishing it.

30
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,280
I must thank you properly.

31
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,760
Without your help,

32
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:02,880
this flower wouldn't bloom so beautifully.

33
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,280
This...

34
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,280
Monster!

35
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,520
Catch her!

36
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,160
My Lord.

37
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,920
I will spare your lives for today.

38
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:24,520
From now on, the people of Ercheng belong to me.

39
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,960
Whatever I want them to do,

40
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,800
they will do.

41
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,720
Little ones,

42
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:37,240
you must have been holding back these days.

43
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,880
Go, satisfy your cravings.

44
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:42,200
Thank you, Master.

45
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,040
My Lord!

46
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,760
My Lord!

47
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:09,760
I

48
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:13,480
have failed the Emperor's grace and the people.

49
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,120
I am so sorry to you all.

50
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,080
My Lord!

51
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,600
This woman is so vicious.

52
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,200
They massacred the city for a whole day.

53
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:39,120
It was a bloodbath, too horrible to look at.

54
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:43,760
Magistrate Shen felt ashamed for failing the people,

55
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,720
so he hanged himself.

56
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,980
Unexpectedly,

57
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:51,080
the demoness Ruixi ate Magistrate Shen's body raw,

58
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,920
and ordered her demons to share it.

59
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,400
It was truly cruel

60
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:59,360
and outrageous.

61
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,080
After this disaster,

62
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:07,360
only Head Constable Guo and I survived in the government office.

63
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,200
Since then, Ruixi stopped pretending

64
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,520
and openly forced the people to be slaves,

65
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,800
ordering them around.

66
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,160
On the other hand, she created an illusion

67
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,200
of peace and prosperity in the city,

68
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:24,080
tricking visitors from all over into staying.

69
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:27,080
Her intentions are truly evil.

70
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,680
No wonder it was so lively

71
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,409
when we first entered the city.

72
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:41,960
We have sent letters to the Sitian Tower in the capital for help many times,

73
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,760
but there has been no news at all.

74
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,400
Today, by fate,

75
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:48,930
please save the people of Ercheng from this suffering, Master.

76
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,880
Since the monsters are so arrogant,

77
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,810
we will definitely not sit idly by.

78
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,560
Exactly.

79
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,560
Even if the Taoist priest doesn't care today,

80
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,890
I will definitely vent this anger for you.

81
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,000
She's here.

82
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,720
We finally

83
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,600
meet.

84
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,020
Magistrate Gu.

85
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,730
Where did you invite

86
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,360
these masters from?

87
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,000
Witch Ruixi,

88
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,000
you have plagued Ercheng for years,

89
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,520
leaving the people in misery.

90
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:33,400
Today, we invited Master Qingxuan to capture you.

91
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,920
Hahaha.

92
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,840
How ridiculous.

93
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,080
Ercheng is in this state today

94
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,960
entirely because of your greed.

95
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:46,480
Why blame me?

96
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:49,340
If your own momentary desires

97
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,000
bring about evil consequences,

98
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,960
you really have no one else to blame.

99
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,680
But you

100
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:57,200
deceived, coerced, and lured them.

101
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,560
For these evil consequences,

102
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,960
you cannot escape blame.

103
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:06,320
Forget it. There's no reasoning with you.

104
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:11,480
But I am willing to give you one last chance.

105
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:15,400
You're quite skilled,

106
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:18,880
and rather handsome.

107
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:22,360
Why don't you stay in Ercheng

108
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:25,560
and share this glory with me?

109
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,720
What a joke.

110
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:29,760
How could Master Qingxuan be bewitched by a little demoness like you?

111
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,960
Instead, I advise you

112
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,560
to kneel down and admit your mistakes.

113
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:34,400
So we can leave your body intact.

114
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:40,960
This is also the master's will.

115
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:43,160
You have brought disaster to this region.

116
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:43,880
Today,

117
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,960
I will purge your evil thoughts

118
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,890
to guide you to the righteous path.

119
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,680
Alright.

120
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:53,520
I want to see how a greenhorn like you

121
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,160
will purge me today.

122
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,360
Kid,

123
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,480
do you still have the amulet I gave you?

124
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,010
Yes, I do.

125
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,200
Tie it to your bow.

126
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:08,640
Okay.

127
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,660
Protect yourself.

128
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,580
So impressive.

129
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:15,480
Ping Jie Qiang Hai Hui.

130
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:15,680
Ping Jie Qiang Hai.
